    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>White pigment made from calcium hydroxyapatite and calcium carbonate derived from bone ash. It was used in grounds for silver point drawings, in making ceramics, and as a polishing compound.</Note_Text>
